JAMES JENKINS v. STATE OF FLORIDA 14 So. (2nd) 843

June Term, 1943

July 23, 1943 Special Division B Rehearing Denied Sept. 14, 1943 Wm. C. Pierce, for appellant. J. Tom Watson, Attorney General, and Woodrow M. Melvin, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

From an examination of the entire record we find no reversible error and the judgment is affirmed.

BUFORD, C. J., TERRELL, BROWN and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
